                  <div className="space-y-4 whitespace-pre-wrap font-sans text-base text-slate-700 leading-loose border-l-4 border-slate-200 pl-6">
                    {record.full_text || "No full content snapshot available. System error during capture."}
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>

            <div className="pt-8 border-t space-y-4">
               <div className="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex gap-3 text-xs text-blue-700 border border-blue-100">
                  <InformationCircleIcon className="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <p className="font-medium leading-relaxed">
                    <strong>重要說明：</strong> 官方政府網址常因系統更新而失效。本系統已為您擷取「監測當下」的內容快照 (Snapshot) 做為 PV 申報之依據。即便外部連結顯示 404，本快照內容仍可作為可追蹤之原始證據。
                  </p>
               </div>
               <div className="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <span className="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-mono italic">
                    Evidence ID: {record.id} // Hash Verified
                  </span>
                  <a href={record.primary_link} target="_blank" className="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 text-xs font-bold hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">
